What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Hospital Gowns Market?

Market Analysis and Insights

Global Hospital Gowns Market

Global hospital gowns market is expected to gain market growth in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research analyses the market to account to USD 5,521.19 billion by 2028 growing at a CAGR of 7.76% in the above-mentioned forecast period. The growing awareness amongst the people and patients regarding the benefits associated with the usage of hospital gowns has been directly impacting the growth of hospital gowns market.

A hospital gown is a type of protective equipment that is used to protect in medical circumstances. Hospital gowns are mainly used to protect the wearer from infectious diseases and if the wearer comes in contact with infectious liquids or elements. It is also used with PPE kits for overall protection from infectious diseases.

Increasing awareness and demand for safety equipment for diseases such as COVID-19 is the main driving factor for the hospital gowns market. Growth in the usage of disposable hospital gowns as a protection control mechanism is also a driver for the hospital gowns market. An increase in healthcare infrastructure for patient’s safety is an opportunity for the hospital gowns market. Advancements in government policies for the safety and hygiene of the patients are also expected to grow the hospital gowns market.

The reuse of the hospital gown in hospitals is a challenging factor for the gowns market. However, the increase in usage of fake hospital gowns and government policies regarding the raw material used for hospital gowns is the main restraint to the hospital gowns market growth during the forecast period of 2021-2028.

